org.apache.juneau.plaintext

Class PlainTextParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juneau.CoreObject
      • org.apache.juneau.parser.Parser
        • org.apache.juneau.parser.ReaderParser
          • org.apache.juneau.plaintext.PlainTextParser

  • @Consumes(value="text/plain")
public class PlainTextParser
extends ReaderParser
    Parsers HTTP plain text request bodies into Group 5 POJOs.
    Media types:
    Handles Accept types: text/plain

    Produces Content-Type types: text/plain

    Description:
    Essentially just converts plain text to POJOs via static fromString() or valueOf(), or through constructors that take a single string argument.

    Also parses objects using a transform if the object class has an PojoSwap<?,String> transform defined on it.

    Configurable properties:
    This class has the following properties associated with it:
    • ParserContext
